 rags weighed and - perhaps they'd - give us four}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3547903\charrsid2953716  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 pence. And we'd go back home and say we got three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
