iform which was a - consisted of a belt and a - a knapsack and your pillbox hat and we used to drill in the - playground of a school. And - and then go out on - Church Parades and march - little processions, march through the streets with your - drum and 
fife band in front of yours. Which would consist of bulles and drums.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Did you enjoy that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Oh yes. I loved it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Were there any kind of rules of conduct and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 No, not really. No, not - no there wasn't, but we used to hav
e to have - Church parades and - on a Sunday, which I thought was a very good thing 'cos - you used to go to different churches you see. But - a quite a distance away would be four or five miles you'd march - to a particular church.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Would boys from all different churches all be in the one Brigade and then they would go to different churches?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 No, no, it'd be one Brigade from - one particular church to another church. To a service Sunday morning service it used to be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Did your church run any temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 You weren't encouraged not to drink through the church or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Any other clubs you remember at the church, or any clubs or organisations to do with the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Well I did because I was a young man then when I joined the church club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Not in your teens anymore?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 No, not in the teens, there was no - to be honest about it there was never such things anyway. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Nothing for women either, like a sewing circle or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Oh yes, there used to be - what they call the Mother's Meeting wasn't there. For mothers and some - one after - particular afternoon. Yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Did your mother go, do you remember her going along?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 No,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 So you think there were some but you don't actually remember your mother going?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Yes, I think - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Do you remember if you were taught to say prayers at night?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Yes. Oh yes, we used to have to say our prayers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 It was an individual thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 You were saying about St Luke's church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Well St Luke's church you see, they was quite - a wealthy - family in - in - West End of London that had interest in St Luke's ch
urch. And that's where they - used to get all their clothes from.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Was this family collecting clothes from other people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Well the - these - these ladies used to come to - I can't think of the name of the place - Boyd's Institute. It was call Boyd
's Institute, that was affiliated to St Luke's wasn't it. Belonged to 'em. And there was certain ladies that done welfare work, like you would get - only with - with a name to it now - and they used to go up amongst their friends in Mayfair and all that w
ay and fetch these - lovely clothes down, and they were supposed to be distributed amongst the people that - couldn't afford to buy clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Were they quite good quality clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Do you remember people getting them, do you remember them actually being distributed?
