Well - dockies. Nearly all dock - dock labourers. And - stevedore labourers and - coalies, that used to coal the ships. 'Course you could always pick 
them out because they used to walk about with a big shovel on their - shoulder with a - huge great tin sheet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 What sort of clothes did the dockers were normally?
