\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Did your parents put up posters?
