 at school - instead of paying tuppence for going to the swimming pool - you only paid a penny. Used to go there every Friday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Did you go on your own or with your brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 On me own, no, always on my own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Were you free to play with anyone you liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 You never remember your parents warning you off of a particular child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Do you remember that some parents did that or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 No, not really, but - there might be a quarrel and the mother would c
ome out and - tick you all off and tell him he's not to play with 'em anymore and all this business, but - that was the - individual mothers. The majority of mothers just didn't - bother. The old saying was, the kids could fight one day and be friends the
 next.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 There weren't any people who thought themselves better than other people and said their children must keep apart from them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 No. Not - not in our - district or street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 You were in the Boys Brigade and you liked swimming, any other interests or hobbies that you remember, anything you took an interest in?

