 hung up in the hall. And exhibitions I think I - I never went to them but - some of my paintings were put on the - public hall exhibition.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 When you say it was in the family was it on both sides of the family?
