\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Yes. And of course - I had other - my other two brothers was very - very good at it too. YES, but I shall - actually - painting and draw
ing and - mode}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16597183\charrsid2953716 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 
ling was - I loved it and it was my - evil of my background because I - I - I - used to love missing my school lessons. And I used to get all them jobs and I was delighted you see. So I got - I neglected all my schooling. Although I done 'em
 in school. But I used to have to go to a special - session you see and sit and do all this work, such as - a castle, all in plastic - plast}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16597183\charrsid2953716 ic}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
