Well - I do know they got - rough and - one of 'em left home. As a schoolboy. One left home, and - I helped to carry his - tent, what he got, and all his blooming equipment to - Wanstead - no, not Wan
stead, to - Bostal Woods, up on the common there which would be about seven or eight miles away from where he lived. And he was going to live up there. And I helped to carry all his stuff up there and - fixed his tent up. And left him. Of course I went ba
ck home. But what happened after that I don't know but - he did - eventually - he got - bumped off out in Rio de Janeiro in America. In a gang yes, he was - shot. Got killed out there.
