\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 But that was after the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 But when the children were born did a woman come in and help her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 My aunt
. She was a - what they call a - midwife. And that was her - that was her - her profession of earning money. Not a professional - not a - no, she was a - self made one, and she had a doctor had her to follow him, he'd had - you see, you get a doctor gives
 a lot of faith in you and he'd keep you booked up you see. So she was always on them particular jobs. And - I believe, I don't know about myself but I know she had all the dealing with the rest of my family, my two brothers - three brothers and sister.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 She brought you into the world you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Would she then come in every day?
