Every day, oh yes, that was her job then to - stop - recognised a fortnight wasn't it. And that would be her living you see, she'd live - get her money like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 And she was an aunt?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Did your mother pay her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 She would have paid her the standard rate whatever it was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Oh I don't know, I don't know, no, I wouldn't know that.
