\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 No, no bets, no, the bet was - the betting was done in the works because - there was always a - what they call a runner}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
