t dressed he said - he really had came up there to tell me - where to go and he said, now for your misbehaviour down to the garage. And go to work down there. There was somebody - another boy was out sick. And from then on that's where I remained and - an
d 'course he - in a - in a wise way he'd done me a good turn. Because I - that was my - first starting of a good job in there. That's how I came to be on the transport section.
