Eight months. And I worked jolly hard and I lost - lost two stone. I did really work hard. I used to serve petrol. Dewax cars, that was new cars, all in the same time. Clean out showrooms. The showrooms and po
lish the cars. And server petrol. And when I left there - another - chap took my place - and - funny enough I'd worked with the follow that did - got a garage - a house next door, and he picked up the ticket of the forecourt attendants ticket and his mone
y was - thirteen pound. See, that that's how they exploited me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14497874 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 Was he a younger man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2099306 FK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6825497\charrsid2953716 No, not really, he was - he come from Clacton, he was a business man gone broke. He done more hours. He done seven days a week.
